data.name: Quick Vegetarian Borscht
data.quickTastyDescription: A comforting and vibrant beet soup, packed with flavor and nutrients, perfect for a quick meal!
detailedCookingInstructions: In a large pot, heat olive oil over medium heat.
Add chopped onion and minced garlic, saut√© until fragrant and translucent.
Stir in diced beets, carrots, and potatoes, and cook for about 5 minutes.
Pour in vegetable broth and bring to a boil.
Reduce heat and add shredded cabbage; simmer for 20 minutes or until all vegetables are tender.
Serve hot, garnished with fresh dill and a dollop of sour cream.
